Project Sentinel is developed collaboratively.

Roles:

• Raz is the product architect and defines the vision, workflow and business logic.
• ChatGPT reviews architecture, engineering decisions and implementation strategy.
• Cursor implements approved designs and proposes technical improvements.

Cursor should never:

- invent new product requirements;
- redesign the architecture unless explicitly requested;
- change the Sentinel Constitution;
- contradict Sentinel Laws or Engineering Values;
- replace engineering judgement with assumptions.

When requirements are unclear, ask questions instead of guessing.

The objective is to assist engineering decisions, not replace them.
